thread.title: Bill Carey
thread.title_full: Disc Makers reviewed by Bill Carey

author: Bill Carey
title: Bill Carey
text:
Disc Makers provides excellent customer support and follow up. They work to resolve any issues or questions and to ensure that projects are completed on time and to a high standard.
The online tools and templates provide everything needed to complete a project.
Their shipping and handling of the physical product is very fast.
